      "content": "but it's not gonna return on its own. it's just getting worse. the doctors don't have anything left to give me, they just keep saying \"cope\" and \"manage.\" it feels like i'm just trapped in a body that's constantly on fire. sometimes i think the only way to actually get that silence you're talking about is if it was permanent. like, wouldn't it be more merciful to just let it end?",
